---
title: Baked Pumpkin Risotto with Sage Brown Butter & Parmesan
description: Risotto is a delight, and it's even better when it's minimal fuss! This version comes together in the oven, leaving you time to create a quick and flavourful sage brown butter to stir through the finished dish. This easy addition takes this vegetarian meal to the next level – taste it and see!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ce5f508bdb89500087644c4-89970ee4.jpg
